name: Kabaddi 4: The Final Match
overview: Kabaddi 4: The Final Match, also known as Kabbadi 4 and कबड्डी ४: द फाइनल म्याच is a 2022 Nepali romantic comedy film, directed by Ram Babu Gurung. The film is produced by Mani Ram Pokharel, Om Chand Rauniyar and Sushma Gurung under the banner of Baasuri Films.
